title: #190: Candyman Candyman Candyman (@DeanDelray)
itunes:title: Candyman Candyman Candyman with Dean Delray
description: Dean Delray came over to my Los Angeles AirBnB to discuss a great love we both share. Candy. It's our muse. Seriously, we're both highly addicted to candy and we can't stop eating it but this is more a celebration of the thing we love. From how we got started on the sugar highway, to how it makes us feel, to our all time favorites. This is all about that sweet sweet.
